[{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"<https://groups.google.com/d/msg/vim_dev/2AaZMN1T6K8/upsbbZUFAgAJ>\noptimize-directxブランチで速度改善したという報告。よかった。\n問題はこれをBramがマージしてくれるかというところだな。","ts":"1513991223.000067","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"+1","count":1,"users":["U06BRP8VD"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"ところで、完全にDirect2Dに移行する場合、スクロールはどうすればいいのだろう。ID2D1RenderTarget::CreateBitmap でビットマップを作ってから、ID2D1Bitmap::CopyFromRenderTarget で領域をコピーすればいいのだろうか？","ts":"1514002177.000045","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"ゲーム脳で行くと、フルスクリーン再レンダリングです。","ts":"1514002488.000046","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"で、複雑な描画については、描画リスト(コマンド群をパッケージしたもの)を登録しておいて、それを呼び出す。","ts":"1514002534.000034","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U03C4RC8X","text":"ゲーム脳と聞いて","ts":"1514002554.000045","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"3D *ゲーム* (シーン)をレンダリングする *脳*","ts":"1514002582.000028","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U03C4RC8X","text":"フルスクリーン再レンダリングということができます","ts":"1514002649.000045","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"CreateBitmap &amp; CopyFromRenderTarget &amp; DrawBitmap という手はあるとは思うけど、その場合スクロールによる AA への影響がちょっとだけ懸念されるな。","ts":"1514002794.000035","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"Vim のスクロールは縦方向だけだからまず大丈夫だとは思うけど。","ts":"1514002803.000033","edited":{"user":"U06BRP8VD","ts":"1514002815.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"再レンダリングは `:digraphs` が遅いということが分かってしまいましたから、可能であれば避けたいですね。","ts":"1514006748.000033","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"`:digraph` どうして遅いんです? 特定の文字が遅い?","ts":"1514006801.000062","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"計ってないので分からないですね。特定の文字なんですかね？","ts":"1514006882.000038","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"もしくは…純粋にびっしり書かれるから遅いとかかな。","ts":"1514006947.000006","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"`:dig` の結果を3回分ほどバッファにコピーして `:set nomore`, `:%p` で表示してみたら、ASCIIの辺りは速くて、絵文字の辺りは遅いですね。","ts":"1514007405.000056","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U6XP9LZ6V","text":"<https://github.com/vim/vim/issues/2489>\nもっと情報書いて！","ts":"1514007590.000046","attachments":[{"fallback":"GitHub: Characters not rendered properly with DirectX · Issue #2489 · vim/vim","id":1,"title":"Characters not rendered properly with DirectX · Issue #2489 · vim/vim","title_link":"https://github.com/vim/vim/issues/2489","thumb_url":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/1585463?s=400&v=4","blocks":null,"service_name":"GitHub","service_icon":"https://a.slack-edge.com/bfaba/img/unfurl_icons/github.png","thumb_width":250,"thumb_height":250,"from_url":"https://github.com/vim/vim/issues/2489"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"}]
